-- Prisma-level migration note:
-- `User.id`, `Client.id`, and `Contact.id` now use `@default(cuid())` in
-- `server/prisma/schema.prisma`.
--
-- `cuid()` is generated by Prisma Client rather than by a native PostgreSQL
-- column default, so this migration intentionally has no SQL statements.
--
-- After pulling this change, run:
--   npm run db:generate --workspace server
--   npm run db:push --workspace server
-- and restart the server process.
